title: Safariland Duty Gear Bianchi 78-83-4PBL: 78 Glock 17/22 Bsk Blk, Basket Weave, Black
features: Magazines are oriented “bullets out” to save space on belt
Optimal for use on tactical rigs due to minimal width
description: The Model 78 Slimline Double Magazine Pouch is designed to carry two magazines on a 2.25" (58mm) duty belt. The 78 features both vertical and horizontal belt slots, allowing it to ride in either a vertical or low-profile horizontal position. A magazine tension screw located between the two pouches allows for easy retention adjustment. It's constructed of rugged SafariLaminate and is available in several scuff-resistant finishes with four different closures.
